These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating kiwi and the person who's sport is weightlifting have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | kiwi | cucumber  |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola
There 2 different types of food: banana, strawberry
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating banana have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | cola      | hot-chocolate       |
| Food       | strawberry | banana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, classical
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, skateboarding
1. the fan electronic and the person who's sport is snowboarding have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | classical     | electronic       |
| Sport         | snowboarding | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, chinese
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the chinese and the person who's sport is ice-hockey have different parity positions##9
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | chinese | colombian |
| Sport         | golf | ice-hockey  |

 #################################

 
